<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n06040k"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n06" href="#n06040k">N06 (VI.B.11)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n06all.htm#n06040k"> 40(k)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> altro (cat &amp; ball)</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">le petit gar&ccedil;on qui se bat avec d&apos;autres et qui &ldquo;ne peut pas plus s&apos;emp&ecirc;cher de courir apr&egrave;s un autre gar&ccedil;on qui a pass&eacute; pr&egrave;s de lui en courant qu&apos;un petit <mark>chat</mark> ne peut s&apos;emp&ecirc;cher de courir apr&egrave;s une <mark>balle</mark> qui roule &hellip;. <font color="green">[he little boy who fights with others and who cannot help but run after another boy who has passed by him running is like a small cat who cannot help but run after a ball that rolled &hellip;]</font> <small> Fr&eacute;d&eacute;ric Queyrat, <a name="FQLJ" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#FQLJ"><cite title="source">Les Jeux des Enfants</cite></a> (1920) 35</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
